# Drop your PDF, DOCX, or Markdown documents here.
# Run `python scripts/generate_sample_docs.py` to populate with realistic test documents.
# Organize files into subdirectories by department:
#
#   data/sample_docs/
#     hr/           → HR policies, handbooks
#     engineering/  → Tech docs, runbooks
#     finance/      → Expense, budget policies
#     legal/        → Compliance, data policies
#     general/      → IT, security, general company docs
#
# The subdirectory name becomes the `department` metadata field,
# which can be used as a filter in API queries.
